# Repo-root brain/ and CLAUDE.md are local-only:
# (1) Maintainers dogfood project-brain to manage project-brain itself —
#     ./brain/ is our own project state, not for the public repo.
# (2) Contributors testing the templates locally inside this repo
#     would also produce a ./brain/ they shouldn't commit.
# Either way: templates/brain/ is the canonical source; ./brain/ is private.
/brain/
